I had the idea of reformating the ebook Tyranids codex from ~GeeDubs into a TiddlyWiki, which makes a more usable format that's easier to search through and reference data through. It's incomplete, and I still need more data to pull from the 40k BRB, but it serves most of my purposes admirably. It's cool, but if you don't know how to play 40k, then it's mostly meaningless to you, unless you want to read the fluff (which is also pretty much freely available via Lexicanum or 1d4chan).

Link to the codex is <a href="./codex-tyranids.html">here</a>.